    "选一家 provider 给你的语音转录做后期清理。每家 key 独立存储，可随时切换。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "Pick a provider to clean up your transcripts. Each key is stored separately; switch any time." } }
      }
    },
