    },
    "勾选你会说的语言。勾得越多越容易误判（比如把中文听成日文）。至少保留一个；默认中 + 英。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "Check the languages you speak. The more you enable, the more likely Soniox will mis-detect (e.g. hearing Chinese as Japanese). Keep at least one; defaults to Chinese + English." } }
      }
    },
    "不可修改" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "Read-only" } }
      }
    },
    "默认风格已经写好。发给 AI 的是英文版（识别效果最好），上面显示的是中文翻译。想改成自己的风格，复制到下面的自定义版本里改。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "The default style is ready to use. The version sent to AI is in English (best results); above shows a Chinese translation. To customize, copy it into one of the slots below and edit." } }
