    },
    "新账号有免费额度，先用着不要钱。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "New accounts get free credit — costs nothing to start." } }
      }
    },
    "每天有免费配额，量不大的话不用付钱。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "Daily free quota — usually no payment needed for casual use." } }
      }
    },
    "免费额度大、速度飞快。适合刚开始试。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "Generous free tier and very fast. Great to try first." } }
      }
    },
    "质量最稳，但要先充钱才能用。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "Most consistent quality, but requires prepaid credit." } }
      }
    },
    "知名度最高，但价格不便宜，要先充值。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "Most well-known but pricier — requires prepaid credit." } }
      }
    },
    "关于" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "About" } }
      }
    },
    "版本" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "Version" } }
      }
    },
    "说一段话 → 实时转成文字 → AI 整理通顺 → 复制给 ChatGPT / Claude / 任何 Agent。打字慢的时候用。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "Speak → live transcript → AI cleans it up → copy to ChatGPT / Claude / any agent. For when typing is too slow." } }
      }
    },
    "隐私" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "Privacy" } }
      }
    },
    "你填进去的 API key 只存在这台手机的 keychain 里，我们看不到，也不会上传。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "Your API keys are stored only in this phone's Keychain. We never see them or upload them." } }
      }
    },
    "录音通过你自己的 Soniox key 发到 Soniox，整理通过你自己的 AI 厂商 key 发到对应厂商。中间不经过任何我们的服务器。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "Audio is sent to Soniox via your own Soniox key; cleanup runs through your own AI-provider key. Nothing routes through our servers." } }
      }
    },
    "热词、自定义整理风格、设置项都只存在本机。" : {
      "localizations" : {
